<p class="gcf-txt-article">　</p>
<h2 class="gcf-ttl-h2"> <span class="gcf-ttl-h2__text">第一弾募集で寄附をいただいた方より</span></h2>
<h3 class="gcf-ttl-h3--border"><span class="gcf-ttl-h3__text">この取組みを応援します</span></h3>
<figure class="lyt-image">
<img src="https://img.furusato-tax.jp/img/x/gcf/project/form/details/20180910/gpfd_24aff5960c8952bda2b22241770c185987344f66.jpg" />
